creator: Life Time, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The Life Time Training app helps you achieve your fitness goals by delivering personalized programs created by certified Life Time Personal Trainers. Life Time Training will help you stay committed to a Healthy Way of Life through comprehensive training plans, interactive messaging and progress reports.

IN APP MESSAGING
Stay accountable through instant messaging with your Trainer and in app Community Groups.

CUSTOM PROGRAMS
Created by a certified Life Time Personal Trainer, your program will be customized to your goals and abilities.

EXERCISE VIDEO LIBRARY
View videos of every exercise prescribed by your Personal Trainer to see proper form and technique.

WORKOUT CALENDAR
See a calendar view of your program to know what is coming and what you've already accomplished.

PROGRAM TRACKING
Track your cardio and strength workouts, body measurements and tasks to stay motivated.

PROGRESS TRACKING
Take progress photos and record lifting measurements as you progress through your plan.

NUTRITION TRACKING
Sync with Fitbit or MyFitnessPal to track your daily nutrition.

appDetails.developerAddress:
Life Time, Inc.
2902 Corporate Place
Chanhassen, MN 55317
appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Consistency is key with this release! Introducing habit streaks and achievement badges—a new way to motivate clients to build healthy habits! Clients can create habit winning streaks by completing a habit every day that it’s scheduled into their calendars. As their streak continues to grow, they'll unlock special achievement badges at various milestones. 

As always, we've also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.

With On-demand Video Workouts, trainers can create follow-along classes and workouts and deliver new ways for clients to get their sweat on. We’ve also released workouts of the day (WODs), workouts that trainers can share in groups that include a live participant feed. Meanwhile, Video Call

creator: Life Time, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The Life Time Training app helps you achieve your fitness goals by delivering personalized programs created by certified Life Time Personal Trainers. Life Time Training will help you stay committed to a Healthy Way of Life through comprehensive training plans, interactive messaging and progress reports.

IN APP MESSAGING
Stay accountable through instant messaging with your Trainer and in app Community Groups.

CUSTOM PROGRAMS
Created by a certified Life Time Personal Trainer, your program will be customized to your goals and abilities.

EXERCISE VIDEO LIBRARY
View videos of every exercise prescribed by your Personal Trainer to see proper form and technique.

WORKOUT CALENDAR
See a calendar view of your program to know what is coming and what you've already accomplished.

PROGRAM TRACKING
Track your cardio and strength workouts, body measurements and tasks to stay motivated.

PROGRESS TRACKING
Take progress photos and record lifting measurements as you progress through your plan.

NUTRITION TRACKING
Sync with Fitbit or MyFitnessPal to track your daily nutrition.
